MaildirStore drivendata-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/drivendata/
Inbox ~/.mail/drivendata/Inbox

Channel drivendata
Master :drivendata-remote:
Slave :drivendata-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Trash"
Create Both
# Expunge Both
SyncState *
# MaxMessages 1000
ExpireUnread no